quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,74,"““Ndipo kumbukirani pamene (Allah) adakupangani kukhala amlowammalo pambuyo pa mtundu wa Âdi. Ndipo adakukhazikani pa dziko (mwa ubwino). Mukudzimangira nyumba zikuluzikulu mchigwa, ndiponso kusema ndi kuboola mapiri kukhala nyumba. Choncho kumbukirani mtendere wa Allah, ndipo musaononge pa dziko pofalitsa chisokonezo.”"
  7,75,"“Adanena akuluakulu omwe adali odzitukumula mwa anthu ake kuuza omwe adaponderezedwa kwa amene adakhulupirira mwa iwo: “Kodi muli ndi chitsimikizo kuti Swalih ngotumizidwa ndi Mbuye Wake (wapatsidwa utumiki)?” (Iwo) Adati: “Ndithu ife tikukhulupirira zomwe watumidwa nazo (kuzifikitsa kwa ife).”"
  7,76,"“Omwe adadzitukumula adati: “Ndithu ife tikuzikana zomwe mwazikhulupirirazo.”"
  7,77,"“Choncho adaipha (adaizinga) ngamira ndi kunyoza lamulo la Mbuye wawo, nati: “E iwe Swaleh! Tibweletsere (chilango) chimene wakhala ukutilonjeza ngati ulidi mmodzi wa otumidwa.”"
  7,78,"“Choncho, chivomerezi chidawagwira mwadzidzidzi, adapezeka ali akufa chigwadire m’nyumba zawo"
  7,79,"“Tero, Swalih adawasiya (nkupita kwina kwake) uku akunena: “E anthu anga! Ndidafikitsadi uthenga wa Mbuye wanga kwa inu. Ndipo Ndidakuchenjezani ndi kukulangizani. Koma inu simufuna alangizi.”"
  7,80,"“Nayenso Luti (tidamtuma, ndipo kumbuka) pamene adati kwa anthu ake: “Kodi mukuchita chonyansa chomwe sadakutsogolereni aliyense kuchichita mwa anthu akale m’zolengedwa zonse?”"
  7,81,"““Ndithu inu mukuwadzera amuna mwa chilakolako kusiya akazi! Ndithudi, inu ndinu anthu olumpha malire.”"